section.bio#bio

	//- title
	.bio-title-container
		h2.title.title--md.bio-title Bio
			span.title__period .

	//- content container
	.bio-content-container

		//- composite
		.bio-composite-container
			.bio-composite.hide
				img.bio-composite__image(src='../images/headshot_min.png', alt='')

		//- about
		article.article.bio-article
			h3.article__title.title.title--sm About
			p.article__copy I build carefully-crafted web experiences. My process begins by identifying the primary call to action of a project. I then use a number of tools that devolve gracefully into efficient HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. I tend to favor a minimalistic style both visually and in code. As a web developer in an ever-evolving field, I work hard to stay in touch with emerging technologies, and design trends. If you have any projects or opportunities, please get in touch!

			//- skills
			.skills.bio-skills
				h3.skills__title.title.title--sm Skills
